1. *Dušo* nam je donela slatkiše. (She brought us sweets.)
2. Oči su joj sijale kao *duše*. (Her eyes were shining like stars.)
3. *Dušo* moja, sve će biti u redu. (My love, everything will be fine.)
4. Prepoznao sam je po *duši*. (I recognized her by heart.)
5. Otvorio je oči i vidio *dušu*. (He opened his eyes and saw a soul.)